---
description: Frontend theme + styling conventions (keep UI modern)
globs: frontend/src/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

1. Theme usage: use `ThemeProvider` for light/dark mode and `ThemeWrapper` + `ThemeRegistry` for per-route accent; global color tokens live in `frontend/src/index.css`.
2. Styling: prefer semantic Tailwind tokens/classes (`bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, etc.) or include matching `dark:` variants for any fixed color.
3. CSS constraint: do not create new `*.css`/`*.scss` files; only edit `frontend/src/index.css` for global theming/token changes.
4. MUI (if introduced): prefer Material UI `sx={{ ... }}` for styling (avoid `style` prop and inline CSS).
